Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:36.34,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The appearance of defectors\Naboard the Macross
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:39.08,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,has raised the possibility of coexistence\Nwith the Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:44.28,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing a glimmer of hope, Misa\Nresolves to travel to Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:46.80,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,to persuade those at UN High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:53.89,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(81,134)}GOODBYE GIRL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:08.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Pull yourself together, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:13.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you'll be able to convince\Nthem looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:16.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, that's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell Lieutenant Ichijo\Nthat you're going to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:31.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll find out eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:38.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The shuttle is ready for launch.\NIt is scheduled to depart in fifteen minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:41.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Zentradi movements?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.17,0:02:43.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No movement detected from\Npoint A-4 onward, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No change, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:49.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope they don't launch another attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.80,0:02:53.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain's pretty restless, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:56.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone here who's\Neven more restless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.52,0:03:02.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie Violet Squadron!\NPrepare to begin your landing sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How's everything going, Shammy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:09.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Excuse me, but please don't\Ntalk to me while I'm giving orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.39,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding. She even forgot to say,\N"No smoking on the bridge!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:21.20,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Escort squadron, prepare to launch\Nin three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. Captain Hayase's stand-in is Shammy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:27.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can that kid handle it?\NThe rumor is she's kind of a screw-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They mounted FAST Packs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:48.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the communicator?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.63,0:04:16.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it connect to the ship's internal phone line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:19.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you don't mind voice-only.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your call is being connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:28.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:29.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:33.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain? Um, I've got the day off, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't about work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:39.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.91,0:04:43.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to leave for Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:51.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking all the data we've acquired\Nto try to persuade High Command
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,to end the war with the Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:56.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No one told me about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If it got out that I was heading back to Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:03.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,it could cause unrest among\Nthe civilians on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers using special\Nauthority to return to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how they'd see it.\NSo this had to be top-secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:11.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, where are you right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:16.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I go back, I may not be able\Nto return to the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I wanted to at least\Nsay goodbye to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, where are you calling from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:26.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Ichijo, please look after\Nour Zentradi defectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:30.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still a lot of people who\Ndon't understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.94,0:05:34.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:36.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Captain Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuttle escort squadron is now launching.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:13.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! An enemy detachment has\Nsuddenly moved into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.47,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they've detected the shuttle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:19.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have the shuttle change course!\NEvade the enemy forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:20.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack! We are changing course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy fighters are approaching\Nfrom 1 o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:35.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Units 4, 5, and 6, break off\Nand delay the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:36.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:42.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! An enemy formation has altered course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:45.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It worked. All right, men... Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.52,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy pods have appeared at 2 o'clock high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're closing on the shuttle, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:07:00.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Units 5 and 6, head to point Lambda 0-3-4\Nand rejoin the main shuttle group!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those first ones were decoys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinforcements for the escort\Nsquadron are {\i1}en route!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:24.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The shuttle is surrounded!\NApproximately sixty enemy pods!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How long until those reinforcements get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At maximum thrust, twenty minutes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:34.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shammy! Deploy the Booby Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:35.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Booby...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.37,0:07:38.64,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The mechanics will know what it means.\NNow hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:40.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And have Lieutenant Ichijo pilot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:41.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.91,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, step on it! At this rate,\NI'm not gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:54.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,First Lieutenant Ichijo, your target\Nis point Lambda 0-3-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:56.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of that location!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.36,0:07:57.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:01.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you tell him the new codes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:06.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I never thought he'd have to\Nsortie on his day off, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.29,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Ichijo, I'll use\Nthe old code system.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:15.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please head to point A3-102 immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:32.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, that's thirty down, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:38.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:00.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Incoming message from escort squadron:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:03.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"The enemy pods have been destroyed.\NWe're returning to base."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:06.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lt. Ichijo is staying behind\Nto escort the shuttle."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:11.10,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just about had enough of standing in\Nfor Captain Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:16.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you certainly appear to have recovered\Nfrom your little code mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:20.29,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good lesson for Shammy to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:23.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we give her a break this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Captain has spoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an incoming transmission\Nfrom First Lieutenant Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you got hit pretty hard.\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ichijo. You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:47.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You said before that you might not\Ncome back to the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:50.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a living witness, someone who knows\Nthe truth about the Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,High Command may not let me\Ngo so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:57.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though your father's an\Nadmiral in the UN Forces?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:10:01.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any special treatment just\Nbecause of who my father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:10.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:15.29,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be thanking you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:18.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This whole time, you've helped us all so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.53,0:10:21.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all I've done is complain about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're a great controller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to begin reentry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's signaling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:43.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I hope... you complete... your mission..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:49.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"and can... safely... return... to the... Macross."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:52.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Hikaru... Ichijo"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:32.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral, are you ready to greet the shuttle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:36.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be awaiting you at Elevator 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.77,0:11:59.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral! The shuttle is twenty\Nminutes behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you care to return to the control tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. I'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.59,0:12:16.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about gloomy.\NYou'd think he was at a wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:22.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,First Lieutenant Ichijo, it's too soon\Nto start getting depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Captain Hayase will make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:29.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not thinking about the captain.\NAnd I'm not depressed either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:33.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, at times like this, it's best\Nto go someplace fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.75,0:12:36.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:44.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At least with you, I'll have a\Ndecent opponent. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:48.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks. I don't think I could beat you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:52.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll find you a one-player game. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:36.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,UN Forces Captain Misa Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:40.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,By order of Captain Bruno J. Global,\NI stand ready with my report, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:43.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.71,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Thief! Mr. Thief! Mr. Thief! Mr. Thief!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:08.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of fun! Right, Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.76,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:25.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, machines 16 and 7 are\Nabout to get cleaned out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I never shoulda opened an arcade\Non the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:42.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So we and the Zentradi have almost\Nidentical genetic makeup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:47.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If this report is true, we may have to change\Nour attitude toward the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:51.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll persuade the military to\Nenter into peaceful negotiations?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:53.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:05.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,With a little practice, I'm sure you'll\Nbe able to do better, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:19.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could I try a game against you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you've just about cleaned out\Nyour machine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you bet all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.85,0:15:32.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we start at Level B?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.42,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Level A!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:13.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like a good match is going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:26.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, I'm gonna put machine 7's game up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.63,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.24,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.69,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:58.51,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"But let me tell you something:"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.12,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"the Macross has an ace pilot of its own!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:05.47,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this man be the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.63,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:13.23,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Bust of about 85 cm. She's the type\Nto keep 'em wrapped up, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:33.96,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.16,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,This "game" has been my way of life, but I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, leave it to the genius pilot!\NThat was an excellent win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all. She had me\Nsweating for a while there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Miss? Could I get your name\Nand phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:59.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Milia. I have no phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you meet me in Happiness Forest\NPark tomorrow night at 9:00?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:05.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:13.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a real beauty you got a date with!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:28.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral, what did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:33.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They've begun considering how to\Nopen peace negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:45.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been staring at me for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:49.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking how much you\Nlook like your late mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:53.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is there a man in your life yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:04.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what is it you wanted to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at it, Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:15.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we've used the Grand Cannon,\Nour negotiations will proceed smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:20.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This can instantly destroy a fleet\Nof tens of thousands of ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:26.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,When the Zentradi see its power, they'll have\Nno choice but to begin negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:29.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, using this is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:35.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to a Zentradi carrier, the\NGrand Cannon isn't even a child's toy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:39.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This weapon will only make the war worse!\NIt won't serve any purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:44.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the Zentradi will negotiate\Nwithout us having to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:51.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So now a born soldier like you is going\Nto start talking so idealistically?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:55.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the ones who attacked your\Nshuttle are interested in your "peace"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:02.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Their blood and genes may be the same\Nas ours, but they're still aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:04.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaching an understanding\Nwith them won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:10.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, how many thousands of years did\Nhumans fight among themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:13.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,before the formation of the\NEarth UN Government?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:17.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The day has been set for the\Nfiring of the Grand Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:19.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Negotiations will start after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:36.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is it true you haven't left his side\Nfor over a week, Miss Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:37.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:40.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are rumors the two of you\Nare going to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even considered that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:47.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Minmay, what about your old boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:49.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Old boyfriend...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at feigning ignorance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:53.18,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you know who I mean if I mention\Na certain First Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:54.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Hikaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.84,0:20:56.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a good friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:57.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:21:01.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you and Kaifun have been rather close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:04.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange that you've never\Nconsidered marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:07.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Loli, sir, what is this "marriage"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:11.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:15.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredible! They do things even\Nmore amazing than kissing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,More amazing than kissing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:19.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:22.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun, you really haven't proposed to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:23.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:26.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't buy it. Quit hiding the truth and fess up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't getting married, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:34.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, I would not be adverse to the idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:35.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:38.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, stop! You're always joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:40.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}I thought something was up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:40.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What a scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.37,0:21:43.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.61,0:21:44.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.19,0:22:01.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:07.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I need your opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.74,0:22:09.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this tie look good on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:12.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of wearing it\Non my date tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:20.52,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"You mean Hikaru?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.20,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"He's just a good friend!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:30.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing brooding\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.66,0:22:32.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.60,0:22:38.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw Minmay on TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:40.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.26,0:22:41.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:42.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.77,0:22:45.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already got someone who's a\Nbetter match for you than that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:47.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anyone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:48.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:51.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't it be that you just haven't noticed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.55,0:22:55.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of times, people don't see\Nwhat's too close to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.18,0:22:59.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They can get into selfish fights with each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.73,0:23:03.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but deep in their hearts it's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:06.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it was with Roy and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.90,0:23:11.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't find someone like that very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.37,0:23:13.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I wanted to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:16.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you spend all your time here,\Nyou'll catch a cold.
