Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.46,0:23:34.36,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(335,457)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:41.49,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Max and Milia move closer\Nto their third battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.90,0:23:46.74,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia appears before Max at the appointed\Nplace and pulls out a dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.02,0:23:48.32,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,And reflected in her eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.49,0:23:53.54,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,there is burning hatred for an enemy\Nthat has already defeated her twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:57.94,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.05,0:24:00.30,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"VIRGIN ROAD"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:19.18,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:24.87,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:30.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:37.29,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.46,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.63,0:00:49.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:53.22,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:01.56,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:06.87,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:13.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:18.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:24.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:23.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.62,0:24:30.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:36.47,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running to the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.73,0:24:44.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.64,0:24:51.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.34,0:24:56.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.25,0:25:04.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.79,0:25:16.03,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:02.43,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(93,157)}VIRGIN ROAD
